BUSINESS RULE SPECIFICATIONS

RULE INFORMATION

Statement:  A given carpet can only be loaned to one customer at a time 

Constraint: There can be no overlap between the TrialStartDate and TrialEndDate/ActualCarpetReturnDate(whichever is sooner) of two different records in CarpetTrials

